query:
INSERT INTO materials (
  title, description, thumbnailUrl, category, type,
  isPaid, isAvailable, isFeatured, commentsEnabled,
  upvotes, viewCount, downloadCount, favoriteCount, rating, ratingCount,
  createdBy, createdAt, updatedAt
)
SELECT 
  titulo as title,
  descricao as description,
  COALESCE(thumbnail_url, 'https://via.placeholder.com/400x225') as thumbnailUrl,
  COALESCE(category, 'base') as category,
  tipo as type,
  COALESCE(is_paid, 0) as isPaid,
  1 as isAvailable,
  COALESCE(is_featured, 0) as isFeatured,
  1 as commentsEnabled,
  COALESCE(upvotes, 0) as upvotes,
  COALESCE(view_count, 0) as viewCount,
  COALESCE(download_count, 0) as downloadCount,
  0 as favoriteCount,
  COALESCE(rating, 0.00) as rating,
  0 as ratingCount,
  'admin' as createdBy,
  COALESCE(created_at, NOW()) as createdAt,
  COALESCE(updated_at, NOW()) as updatedAt
FROM materiais;
